{
  "stem": "3524.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can remember yet that one of our trucks was told by a sentry, turn out those damn lights or I'm gonna shoot 'em out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we knew we were pretty close.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we ended up in what turned out to be the city, Weimar, which was just outside the Buchenwald concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were then told that we were going to work on liberating some prisoners.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were told-- we were told that they were political prisoners and not American prisoners.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's all that we knew of it at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not the slightest.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Our company commander had said that there was a lot of work to be done and it was a mess up there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't-- weren't aware of what it was until we actually walked in the gates.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the first thing we saw was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [SOBBING] --bodies-- just cartloads of bodies there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SOB] [CRYING] There must have been three or four cartloads of bodies just cross-piled, just waiting outside of a crematorium.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We saw that and we saw the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was still bodies inside the crematorium-- and-- not live, they were shadows and skeletons of bodies.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And later we had a chance to go through some of the living quarters where the living prisoners were still there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were in little cubicles about, oh, four to a section-- 8 by 12, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was so close that they had to lay on their sides.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had no pillows or anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All they had was a-- a metal pan, which they used for their food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was my understanding they had to use that for their evacuation processes as well.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
